# Installation

Learn how to install Docyard on your system.

## Prerequisites

- Ruby 3.2 or higher
- Bundler (recommended)

## Install via RubyGems

```bash
gem install docyard
```


## Install via Bundler

Add to your Gemfile:

```ruby
gem 'docyard'
```


Then run:

```bash
bundle install
```

## Verify Installation

```bash
docyard --version
```


You should see the version number printed to your terminal.

